	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original" xml:lang="de">
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-040_01.png" n="1"/>
					<p>Protokoll</p>
					<p>aufgenommen mit Herrn <persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischhof_frantisek">Franz Fischhof</persName></p>
					<p>geb am: <date when="1898-01-13">13. I. 1898</date></p>
					<p>in: <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/716935/nyiregyhaza.html">Satmar</placeName></p>
					<p>wohnhaft in: <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Prag</placeName> VII., <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">U Smaltovny</placeName> 27.</p>
					<p>gewesener <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-650" type="subject">Häftling</term>: <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Theresienstadt</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-0" type="camp">Auschwitz</placeName>, <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">Kauferring 4</placeName> und <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/3208363/sankt-ottilien.html">St. Ottilien</placeName>.</p>
					<p>Herr <persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischhof_frantisek">Fischhof</persName> gibt an, dass er bestrebt war, die im Block des <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">Lagers</placeName>
						<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">Kauferring 4</placeName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-745" type="subject">verstorbenen</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-650" type="subject">Männer</term> nach streng jüdischem <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Brauch</term> zu reinigen /<term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Taharot</term>/. Auch wurde täglich <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Minian</term> gemacht und die Jahrzeiten [sic!] der <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-758" type="subject">Alt - Neusynagoge</term> abgehalten. So wurde also die <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-758" type="subject">Alt - Neusynagoge</term>
						<q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Al - Tanai</term></q> auch im <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">KZ</placeName> verwirklicht.</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischhof_frantisek">Fischhof</persName></p>
					<p>eigenhändige Unterschrift </p>
					<p>Protokoll aufgenommen:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischerova_marta">Marta Fischerová</persName></p>
					<p>Unterschrift der Zeugen:</p>
					<p>Für die <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">Dokumentationsaktion</term>:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_shek_zeev">Scheck</persName></p>
					<p>Für das Archiv: <date when="1945-10-17">17. X. 1945</date></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schmiedt_alexander">Alex. Schmiedt</persName></p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-040_01.png" n="1"/>
					<p>Protocol</p>
					<p>recorded with Mr. <persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischhof_frantisek">Franz Fischhof</persName></p>
					<p>born on: <date when="1898-01-13">13. I. 1898</date></p>
					<p>in: <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/716935/nyiregyhaza.html">Satmar</placeName></p>
					<p>living in: <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Prague</placeName> VII., <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">U Smaltovny</placeName> 27.</p>
					<p>former <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-650" type="subject">inmate</term>: <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Theresienstadt</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-0" type="camp">Auschwitz</placeName>, <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">Kauferring 4</placeName> and <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/3208363/sankt-ottilien.html">St. Ottilien</placeName>.</p>
					<p>Mr. <persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischhof_frantisek">Fischhof</persName> states that he endeavored to cleanse the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-650" type="subject">men</term> who <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-745"
							type="subject">died</term> in his block of the <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">camp</placeName>
						<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">Kauferring 4</placeName> according to strict Jewish <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">customs</term> /<term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Taharot</term>/. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Minian</term> were also assembled daily and the anniversaries of the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-758" type="subject">Old - New Synagogue</term> were observed. Thus, the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-758" type="subject">Old - New Synagogue</term>
						<q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-736" type="subject">Al - Tanai</term></q> was also realized in the <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-227" type="camp">concentration camp</placeName>.</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischhof_frantisek">Fischhof</persName></p>
					<p>personal signature</p>
					<p>Recorded by:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_fischerova_marta">Marta Fischerová</persName></p>
					<p>Signature of the witnesses:</p>
					<p>For the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">Documentation Campaign</term>:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_shek_zeev">Scheck</persName></p>
					<p>For the archive: <date when="1945-10-17">17. X. 1945</date></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schmiedt_alexander">Alex. Schmiedt</persName></p>
				</div>
			</div>
